12.29.17  7:35 pm   For your next video (to please your fans who can't wait for your whole video to post), could you post it a second at a time?

     i don't think that's a good idea

     Then, your fans could assemble it themselves and watch it as it slowly compiles over weeks and months. What fun! Talk about a loooong reveal. I think this would be a good solution for Rick and Morty fans as well, as it usually takes two years between seasons...  

     that assumes that the production process is 100% complete for each second before the following second is complete, which is really not the way it works. the entirety of the project becomes gradually more complete through each stage, and the final completion of each individual second would likely not be properly achieved until the very last day of production, all at once
